211
00:13:33,574 --> 00:13:37,173
Dia menjatuhkan bola penangkap biasa!

212
00:13:37,174 --> 00:13:39,773
SMU Ohgane sedang memainkan bawah inning ke-10

213
00:13:39,774 --> 00:13:42,873
